<subSubSection pageId="17" pageNumber="725" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="17.[100,1306,1944,2527]" pageId="17" pageNumber="725">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[103,455,2295,2328]" pageId="17" pageNumber="725">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. No additional information on the biology of the Palawan Montane Squirrel has been collected since its description in 1979. There are no major threats from humans because its main habitat has not been disturbed,as it is steep and inaccessible.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
